.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FEERATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-feerate \- show current on-chain fee rates
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-feerate
.RI [ urgent | normal | slow ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns on-chain fee rate estimates from
.B lightning-cli feerates
for the given urgency level (default
.BR normal ).
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"urgency":..., "perkw":{...}, "perkb":{...}}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-onchain-balance (1),
.BR lightning-node-mempool (1)
